OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783700375
OL,3,CFamily plead not guilty to multiple
OL,4,Cweapons offences
OL,6,FA family from Southampton have pleaded
OL,7,Fnot guilty in court to multiple
OL,8,Fweapons offences including possessing
OL,9,F37 swords, flick-knives, an axe and
OL,10,Feight knuckledusters.
OL,12,FVickrum Digwa, 23, appeared by
OL,13,Fvideolink at Southampton Magistrates'
OL,14,FCourt.
OL,16,FHe pleaded not guilty to multiple
OL,17,Fcounts of possessing an offensive
OL,18,Fweapon in a private place at the
OL,19,Ffamily home in St Denys Road,
OL,20,FSouthampton.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/7
