PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783700375
OL,3,CFamily plead not guilty to multiple
OL,4,Cweapons offences
OL,6,FThe alleged weapons are three
OL,7,Fmachetes, 37 swords, three ninja
OL,8,Fswords, two flick-knives or gravity
OL,9,Fknives, eight knuckledusters, an
OL,10,Fextendable baton and a manriki-gusari.
OL,12,FHis father, Moga Singh, 52, and his
OL,13,Fbrother, Gurpreet Digwa, 27, both of
OL,14,FSouthampton, Hampshire, appeared in
OL,15,Fcourt and pleaded not guilty to the
OL,16,Fsame charges while Gurpreet faced four
OL,17,Fadditional charges of which he also
OL,18,Fdenied.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
