FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783700375
OL,3,CFamily plead not guilty to multiple
OL,4,Cweapons offences
OL,6,FThese are possessing an offensive
OL,7,Fweapon in a public place, with the
OL,8,Foffences being possessing an
OL,9,Fextendable baton, a kirpan and an axe
OL,10,Fin a car in Belmont Road, and the
OL,11,Ffourth charge being of possessing an
OL,12,Fair weapon in Belmont Road.
OL,14,FThe court heard all three defendants
OL,15,Fface an additional amended count of
OL,16,Fpossessing three push daggers in a
OL,17,Fprivate place.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783700375
OL,3,CFamily plead not guilty to multiple
OL,4,Cweapons offences
OL,6,FHowever, the charge was not put to
OL,7,Fthem to enter pleas as District Judge
OL,8,FHenry Gordon requested clarification
OL,9,Fon the details of the amendment and
OL,10,Fwhether the offence was charged within
OL,11,Fthe six-month time limit for the
OL,12,Fcharge to be made.
OL,14,FAll of the offences are dated December
OL,15,F4 2025.
OL,17,FJudge Gordon set a trial date for
OL,18,FSeptember 27 2027, with a case
OL,19,Fmanagement hearing on June 4 2027.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
