FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783700375
OL,3,CFamily plead not guilty to multiple
OL,4,Cweapons offences
OL,6,FHe told the three defendants: "You
OL,7,Fhave all pleaded not guilty to the
OL,8,Fcharges that are before the court so I
OL,9,Fadjourn your case for trial.
OL,11,F"You will need to be here for your
OL,12,Ftrial, if you do not it will, in all
OL,13,Flikelihood, take place in your
OL,14,Fabsence."
OL,16,FHe said: "You will need to co-operate
OL,17,Fwith your solicitors so they are ready
OL,18,Ffor your trial date."
OL,26,@nD@_OUsD@AOUvD@IO]xD@JOUzD@UO]
