FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783700375
OL,3,CFamily plead not guilty to multiple
OL,4,Cweapons offences
OL,6,FHe granted Vickrum Digwa technical
OL,7,Funconditional bail until the trial and
OL,8,Freleased his brother and father on
OL,9,Funconditional bail.
OL,11,FJudge Gordon told them: "It means no
OL,12,Fconditions apart from to turn up for
OL,13,Fyour trial, if you do not, you may be
OL,14,Fcommitting a further offence of
OL,15,Ffailing to attend court."
OL,26,@sD@YOUwD@YO]
