FL,389,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F388A1783700375
OL,3,CFamily plead not guilty to multiple
OL,4,Cweapons offences
OL,6,FHarmail Gill, defending the three
OL,7,Ffamily members, told the court that
OL,8,Fsome of the swords in the charges were
OL,9,F"antiques" and that some of the
OL,10,Fweapons were used for "religious
OL,11,Fmartial arts".
OL,13,FThe judge allowed an application from
OL,14,FMr Gill for the current address of
OL,15,FGurpreet Digwa and Singh not to be
OL,16,Fread out in court after the defence
OL,17,Fsolicitor said that they had "moved
OL,18,Ffrom the area for their own safety".
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@JO]rD@WOUsD@MO]yD@^OUzD@cO]
